definition[0]: completely different from a particular person or thing
example[0]: Tammy was unlike any other woman I have ever known.
definition[1]: not typical of someone at all
example[1]: It’s unlike Greg to be late.
definition[2]: used when saying how one person or thing is different from another
example[2]: Unlike most people in the office, I don’t come to work by car.
definition[4]: to show on Facebook that you no longer like or agree with something, after showing that you liked it
